{"type": "article", "id": 29581, "title": "利用飞机座椅布料制作的包", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:09:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160713225237sqSxaFeRPU2uYocz.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>我们之前曾经介绍过几个旧物利用的创意，包括用海洋塑料制成的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28219.html\">太阳眼镜</a>、<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28928.html\">筷子</a>，以及用旧足球制成的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28095.html\">腕带</a>，而最近来自英国的 Ben 和 Harry Tucker 则用一系列漂亮的包和配饰让废弃的飞机座椅得到重生。Plane 是 Tucker 兄弟创立的品牌，所有产品均由座椅织物搭配意大利的植鞣皮革制成。为了呈现织物的历史，废弃之前的飞行里程数、曾经到达过的国家数、飞行高度等数据都和订购者的姓名首字母一起被纹在了每个包上，陪伴新的主人再次踏上旅程。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1346754224/a-new-type-of-luxury-goods-made-from-aeroplanes\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，单品价格从 30 到 280 英镑不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225308l4ua6BbyknQYqCDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132253088IhR3sTzOc2QFtYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132253082PdyNUOWEhibLsz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713225308DhgRH83YVLUFwl5v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}